<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .box {
            width: calc(33.33% - 20px);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .box img {
            max-width: 50%;
            height: auto;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-left: auto; /* Center the image on mobile screens */
            margin-right: auto; /* Center the image on mobile screens */
        }

        /* Media query for smaller screens */
        @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
            .box {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: left;
            }

            .box img {
                max-width: 7rem;
                margin-bottom: 0;
                margin-right: 50; /* Ensure no additional margin on mobile */
            }

            .specific-container .box {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                text-align: center;
                width: calc(100% - 20px);
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .specific-container .content-div {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }

        .specific-container .blackbutton {
            padding: 0.9em 2em;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            color: white;
            background: #333; /* Dark gray button */
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 10px;
            user-select: none;
            -webkit-user-select: none;
            touch-action: manipulation;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 10px; /* Adjusted margin-top */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container specific-container">
        <!-- Box 1 -->
        <div class="box">
            <img src="assets/images/expectantmothers.png" alt="Expectant Mothers" width="340" class="spinonscroll">
            <div class="content-div">
                <h2>Expectant Mothers</h2>
                <p>We strive to cater to our expectant mothers and to make this extremely difficult experience as bright as possible.</p>
                <div>
                    <a href="/expectant-mothers/" class="blackbutton">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Box 2 -->
        <div class="box">
            <img src="/assets/images/housingprogram.png" alt="Housing Program" width="340">
            <div class="content-div">
                <h2>Housing Program</h2>
                <p>We have multiple one-bedroom and two-bedroom apartment units available for our expectant mothers to stay in.</p>
                <div>
                    <a href="/housing-program/" class="blackbutton">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Box 3 -->
        <div class="box">
            <img src="/assets/images/adoptingfamilies.png" alt="Adopting Families" width="340">
            <div class="content-div">
                <h2>Adopting Families</h2>
                <p>While we donâ€™t work directly with families wanting to adopt, we can help point you in the right direction.</p>
                <div>
                    <a href="/adopting-families/" class="blackbutton">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
